-dark:#666666\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><h2 id=\"创建多篇文章\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#创建多篇文章\"><span>创建多篇文章</span></a></h2>\n<p>你可以在<code v-pre>src/content/posts/</code>目录下创建多个Markdown文件，每个文件代表一篇文章。例如：</p>\n<div class=\"vp-file-tree\"><FileTreeNode expanded type=\"folder\" filename=\"src\" :level=\"0\">\n<template #icon><VPIcon provider=\"iconify\" name=\"vscode-icons:folder-type-src\" /></template><FileTreeNode expanded type=\"folder\" filename=\"content\" :level=\"1\">\n<template #icon><VPIcon provider=\"iconify\" name=\"vscode-icons:default-folder\" /></template><FileTreeNode expanded type=\"folder\" filename=\"posts\" :level=\"2\">\n<template #icon><VPIcon provider=\"iconify\" name=\"vscode-icons:folder-type-docs\" /></template><FileTreeNode type=\"file\" filename=\"my-first-post.md\" :level=\"3\">\n<template #icon><VPIcon provider=\"iconify\" name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-markdown\" /></template>\n</FileTreeNode>\n<FileTreeNode type=\"file\" filename=\"my-second-post.md\" :level=\"3\">\n<template #icon><VPIcon provider=\"iconify\" name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-markdown\" /></template>\n</FileTreeNode>\n<FileTreeNode type=\"file\" filename=\"my-third-post.md\" :level=\"3\">\n<template #icon><VPIcon provider=\"iconify\" name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-markdown\" /></template>\n</FileTreeNode>\n</FileTreeNode>\n</FileTreeNode>\n</FileTreeNode></div>\n<p>每篇文章都是一个独立的Markdown文件，文件名将被用作文章的URL路径。</p>\n<h2 id=\"链接多篇文章\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#链接多篇文章\"><span>链接多篇文章</span></a></h2>\n<p>要在博客页面中链接到多篇文章，可以创建一个文章列表：</p>\n<div class=\"language-html line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"html\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\">